button 104 158 1209 1210 1 0 3
button 104 188 1209 1210 1 0 4
button 104 218 1209 1210 1 0 5
button 104 248 1209 1210 1 0 6
button 104 278 1209 1210 1 0 7
button 104 327 1209 1210 1 0 8

[DIALOG D_exp_S TEXT] 
Lady Krystas Experience Giving Staff
This staff is only to be used as a prize.
For winning a Tourney, Or Quest.
1000 EXP
2000 EXP
3000 EXP
4000 EXP
5000 EXP
6000 EXP
7000 EXP
Exit
<SERV.NAME>

[DIALOG d_exp_s BUTTON] 
ONBUTTON=1
SRC.TARG.SOUND 61
SRC.SYSMESSAGE You gave 1k exp to <SRC.TARG.NAME>!
SRC.TARG.SYSMESSAGE <SRC.NAME> just gave you 1k exp!
SRC.TARG.tag.experience=<eval <SRC.TARG.tag.experience> + 1000>
RETURN 1

